==================================
 RsCmwBluetoothSig
==================================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/RsCmwBluetoothSig.svg
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/ RsCmwBluetoothSig/

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/sphinx/badge/?version=master
